    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">普通攻擊</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/07/18/7998136/c9b3491c03cc10af2f8646567d1b7f6e_1053875840751883561.png",
                "id": "talent73695",
                "key": "藏蘊破障",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "藏蘊破障"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素戰技</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: #99FF88\">草元素傷害</span>，本角色附屬<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">通塞識</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">通塞識</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">狀態</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">所附屬角色進行重擊時：</span>造成的<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理傷害</span>變為<span style=\"color: #99FF88\">草元素傷害</span>，並且會在技能結算後召喚<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">藏蘊花矢</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/07/18/7998136/53b113bf04bc84f981d14ad6b81ebedf_5583580639769106173.png",
                "id": "talent18232",
                "key": "識果種雷",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "識果種雷"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成4點<span style=\"color: #99FF88\">草元素傷害</span>，對所有敵方後臺角色造成1點<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">穿透傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/07/18/7998136/d29edf031b7ca4fdce57c099819178d3_8931212028625594389.png",
                "id": "talent40235",
                "key": "造生纏藤箭",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "造生纏藤箭"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">結束階段：</span>造成1點<span style=\"color: #99FF88\">草元素傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數：1（可疊加，最多疊加到2次）</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/04/11/84496276/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_8114568859220423356.png",
                "id": "talent52521",
                "key": "藏蘊花矢",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/17/125391187/610be0cd5a38653316e32f23c8abf0e8_7798373956725091963.png",
                "title": "藏蘊花矢"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">綻放</span>：本傷害+1，生成使下次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>傷害+2的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">「草原核」</span></p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">原激化</span>：本傷害+1，生成「<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">激化領域</span>」</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">草原核</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出戰狀態</span></p><p>我方對敵方出戰角色造成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素傷害</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素傷害</span>時，傷害值+2。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">可用次數：1</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">激化領域</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出戰狀態</span></p><p>我方對敵方出戰角色造成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素傷害</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素傷害</span>時，傷害值+1。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/04/11/84496276/e8cff941b5a0ff248efde360ec9e91fe_3422707578341761063.png",
                "id": "talent97651",
                "key": "草元素傷害·其一",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "草元素傷害·其一"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">燃燒</span>：本傷害+1，召喚<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">燃燒烈焰</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\"><br></span><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">燃燒烈焰</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結束階段：</span>造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：1，最多叠加到2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/04/11/84496276/e8cff941b5a0ff248efde360ec9e91fe_3447509229472046309.png",
                "id": "talent18578",
                "key": "草元素傷害·其二",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/04/11/84496276/3c3362a64ac984342133762388c9eb41_653260399431987160.png",
                "title": "草元素傷害·其二"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理傷害</span></strong></p><p>物理傷害不會附著元素，也不會發生元素反應。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">穿透傷害</span></strong></p><p>穿透傷害無法受到傷害加成，但是也無法被護盾、傷害免疫等效果抵消。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果觸發後，會消耗一層可用次數；</p><p>可用次數耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">重擊</span></strong></p><p>我方元素骰總數為偶數時進行的「普通攻擊」，視為「重擊」。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/04/11/84496276/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_6463261600915999242.png",
